      • setSkewAllowance

        public void setSkewAllowance(int skewAllowance)
        Sets the allowance for time skew in seconds between CAS and the client server. Default 0s. This value will be subtracted from the current time when setting the SAML NotBeforeDate attribute, thereby allowing for the CAS server to be ahead of the client by as much as the value defined here.
        Parameters:
        skewAllowance - allowance in seconds
